<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/377316-anybody-else-out-there-who-finds">Anybody else out there who finds Hemingway&#39;s style almost completely unreadable?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_377316'><a id="like_count_community_question_377316" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/377316?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">78 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F10799.A_Farewell_to_Arms">like</a></span>

