<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/8169636-john-freeman"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1387571309i/8169636._UX100_CR0,1,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/8169636-john-freeman">John Freeman</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Perhaps the dialogue sounds fake because the relationship between Henry and Catherine was fake. I asked myself through the whole book if they really l<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Perhaps the dialogue sounds fake because the relationship between Henry and Catherine was fake. I asked myself through the whole book if they really loved one another. And as tragic as the end was, I somehow felt that Henry, after he grieved, would be relieved he didn't have a child or a wife.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
